    %section#sctn-1
      .banner-1
        .container-1
          .row
            .small-12.columns
              %h2
                From Finance to Media
          .row.about
            .small-12.medium-6.columns
              %p
                It takes a lot of courage to jump from a career to another, but when you do it, the rewards are priceless.
              %p
                In 2009 I've decided to leave my profession in the financial sector to start a new adventure. Since then a lot of things have happened. Take a look to my showreel to have a sneak peak at my editor and designer skills.
            .small-12.medium-6.columns
              %img{:src => "img/banker-editor-cartoon.png", :alt => ""}/
          .row
            .small-12.columns
              .video
                %iframe{:allowfullscreen => "", :frameborder => "0", :height => "315", :src => "https://www.youtube.com/embed/nwySvEfundU", :width => "560"}      
    %section#sctn-2
      .banner-2
        .hanging-pic
          %img{:src => "img/hanging.png", :alt => ""}/
        .container-2
          %h2
            A Jack of All trades
          %p
            Some people may think that a Jack of all Trades is a Master of None, but I'd like to think of myself as a Master of Some.
          %p
            My skills are various and I like to have the ability to change into different roles. It makes life more interesting and I like to be challenged every day.

