    %section#sctn-4
      .banner-4
        .row
          .small-12.columns
            %h2
              Every Sunday I'm on radio...
          .small-6.columns
            %p
              Join the tribe of <a href ="www.kickarts.org.nz">KickArts</a>, Auckland's comprehensive artshow, on air every Sunday on 104.6 FM - Auckland area only - or on the <a href="www.planetaudio.org.nz/kickarts">PlanetAudio</a> website.
            %p
              I've the imponderable joy to be Richard Green's co-host and when he is on holiday I will run the show. It is a fun adventure that is lasting for over 3 years and our audience is growing every week.
          .small-6.columns    
            %p
              Other then working on the show itself I've coded and designed the <a href ="www.kickarts.org.nz">KickArts</a> webpage at <a href ="www.webkea.co.nz">WebKea</a> with the help of my colleague Benji Dalton.
            %p
              Also take a look at <a href ="www.webkea.co.nz">WebKea</a> and discover how you get also get a brilliant online presence for yourself or your business.
    %section#sctn-5
      .banner-5
        .row
          .small-12.columns
            %h2
              Contact me
            %p.contact-info
              Get in touch if you need my help in your project. I'm sure we can find the perfect deal for a great collaboration.
        .row
          .small-12.medium-6.columns
            .contact-pic
              %img{:src => "img/contact-me2.png", :alt => ""}/
          .small-12.medium-6.columns
            .container-5a
              %form.contact-form{:action => "https://getsimpleform.com/messages?form_api_token=a57405a0851707c0d44897fdab40394c", :method => "post"}
                / the redirect_to is optional, the form will redirect to the referrer on submission
                %input{:name => "redirect_to", :type => "hidden", :value => "thankyou.html"}/
                / all your input fields here....
                %p.firstname
                  %input.form-control{:name => "firstname", :required => "", :type => "text"}/
                  %label First Name
                %p.lastname
                  %input.form-control{:name => "lastname", :type => "text"}/
                  %label Last Name
                %p.phone
                  %input.form-control{:name => "phone", :type => "text"}/
                  %label Phone Number
                %p.email
                  %input.form-control{:name => "email", :type => "email"}/
                  %label Email
                %p.message
                  %textarea.feedback{:name => "feedback"}
                %p.submit    
                  %input{:type => "button", :value => "SEND"}/ 
